The paper deals with website fingerprinting attacks, which fall under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper extensively uses deep learning techniques, which makes it likely to be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG) and computer vision (cs.CV) sub-categories. The paper also deals with network infrastructure (cs.NI) and cyber-physical systems (cs.CY) to some extent, as it discusses the fingerprinting of Tor website traces and TLS-encrypted websites.
